author: antoniovagnerini
body: @mtosi  Please note that in order to keep the code tidy in HiggsMonitoring_Client_cff.py, I think it would be better to move the diphotonEfficiency definition in a suitably defined cff file and leave only the paths in the higgsClient sequence, as we did in our case for MssmHbbMonitoring_Client_cff.  Otherwise all private changes by the single groups will be constantly commited to the common HiggsMonitoring_Client_cff.py .
title: HLT DQM MSSM Hbb analysis - rebased
